<H3> <TI>   Rumors About Heightened Radiation Level Refuted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Rumors About Heightened Radiation Level Refuted </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS2505125794 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1000 
