<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS freelance correspondent Semen Ivanov] </F>
  [Text] Moscow, 26 May -- The Cosmos-2281 satellite, 
launched yesterday from Plesetsk cosmodrome by the Tsiklon-3 
booster-rocket, has not been placed into orbit. The ITAR-TASS 
