<H3> <TI>   `Harmony for Latvia' Faction Changes Name </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Harmony for Latvia' Faction Changes Name </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2505200594 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 1900 GMT 25 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2505200594 </F>
<F P=104>  Riga Radio Riga Network </F>
<F P=105>  Latvian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Saeima faction Harmony for Latvia [Saskana 
Latvijai] will in the future be known as the Economic-Political 
Union Faction [Tautsaimnieku Politiskas Apvienibas Frakcija]. 
This was decided today at a session of the faction. The faction 
was formed to unite deputies who were elected to the Saeima from 
a list of 19 candidates and the Economic-Political Union. The 
faction resolved to support the policy consultation formed at 
the initiative of the Harmony for Latvia party from 
center-oriented parties of the right and left, represented and 
not represented in the Saeima. Mentioned as possible 
participants in the consultation are such organizations as the 
Latvian Way, the Democratic Party, the People's Harmony party, 
the Landowner [Saimnieks], the Latvian Social Democratic Party 
of Labor, and Harmony for Latvia. 

</TEXT>

