<F P=102>   PM2705083194 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 27 May 94 
First Edition p 2 </F>

<F P=103> PM2705083194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA </F>
