<H3> <TI>   Social Accord Treaty Signed in Kremlin </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Social Accord Treaty Signed in Kremlin </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2605175394 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1339 GMT 26 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2605175394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow INTERFAX </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Civic Accord Pact in Russia was signed in the 
Kremlin on Thursday. 
  As the head of the President's office, Sergey Filatov, said 
that now the ceremonies for signing the agreement will be held 
in the country's republics, regions and territories. According 
to him, in the month that has passed since the process of 
signing began on April 28, 765 representatives of government 
bodies, Federation members, parties, associations and 
organizations signed the document. 

</TEXT>

