<F P=102>   AU2705090594 Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA in Russian 18 May 94 
p 3 </F>

<F P=103> AU2705090594 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [IPRINDA press agency report under rubric "According to </F>
Reports From Correspondents and Information Agencies": 
"Statement by the Political Council"] 
  [Text] On 17 May, the Georgian Social-Democratic Party 
(GSDP) Political Council disseminated an appeal to the 
republic's population in which an analysis is given of the 
complex sociopolitical situation. Proceeding from this, the 
GSDP Political Council believes: The head of the Georgian state 
should resign and, at the same time, a national salvation 
committee that will be able to implement laws should be formed. 
Otherwise, considers the Political Council, it will be 
impossible to speak about the territorial integrity of Georgia, 
its independence, and the physical salvation of the Georgian 
nation. 

</TEXT>

