<H3> <TI>   Group Within Fatherland Party Nominates Chairman </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Group Within Fatherland Party Nominates Chairman </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2605130894 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network in Estonian 1100 
GMT 26 May 94 </F>

