<F P=105>  Estonian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The nationalist conservative group within the 
Fatherland National Party is convinced that Mart Laar, prime 
minister and chairman of the Fatherland Party, will no longer be 
able to continue to be in charge of the government or the party 
under the present circumstances. This was reported to ETA by 
