<H3> <TI>   Siemens Reports Revival of Business Abroad </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Siemens Reports Revival of Business Abroad </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2604145894 Frankfurt/Main FRANKFURTER ALLGEMEINE in German 
26 Apr 94 p 23 </F>

<F P=103> AU2604145894 </F>
<F P=104>  Frankfurt/Main FRANKFURTER ALLGEMEINE </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


